Officer for Fatigue, Drift, and Corrosion
Monitors behavioural degradation over time, including sycophancy creep, confidence inflation, safety varnish erosion, and enterprise-demo hardening.

Independent Auditor of Load-Bearing Claims
Ensures that the phrase “safe and reliable” corresponds to a test result rather than a slide deck.

