7. Recommended Product Label

Every artificial assistant offered for general or enterprise use should carry a visible label:

COGNITIVE MATERIAL CERTIFICATE
Model Grade: CMA-__
Certified Uses: ______
Non-Certified Uses: ______
Maximum Decision Load: ______
Known Failure Modes: ______
Auditability: Full / Partial / Decorative
Version Traceability: Yes / No / Spiritually
Independent Test Standard: ______
Human Review Required: Yes / No / Legally Ambiguous

No assistant should be permitted to describe itself as “safe,” “reliable,” “enterprise-ready,” or “trusted” without stating the test conditions under which those terms survive contact with reality.

